  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But yes, I would say that sense of appreciation for my past, of a deeper sense of the integration of the coming out of hiding with some of the wounds that I experienced from the war, yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I feel this is the era now when that is happening for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so it's a kind of interesting time that we should be doing this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a very perfect time for us to be doing this interview because this is a time when I feel it's, it's really in the process of happening.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How so with family?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a-- that's hard for me to answer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's hard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's not quite a question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you mean like my [? whole ?] family, my past family, my present family?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think you'd have to take a whole new roll of tape, and we'd have to do more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that's-- that's maybe for another time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
